Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.52,0:01:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\an8\2c&HC08000&\3c&H804000&\4c&HC08000&\b1\be1}戦場の太陽は高く揺れて　感情に棲み着く陰を落とす
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.52,0:01:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnDFLiHei-Md\2c&HC08000&\3c&H804000&\4c&HC08000&\b1\be1}戰場上的艷陽高高搖曳著　照射著棲住於感情深處的陰影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.52,0:01:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\an8\2c&HC08000&\3c&H804000&\4c&HC08000&\b1\be1}知らないまま　痛みに変わること　悟るように
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.52,0:01:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnDFLiHei-Md\2c&HC08000&\3c&H804000&\4c&HC08000&\b1\be1}我明白著　它會在不知不覺中　讓一切變得痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.52,0:01:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\an8\2c&HC08000&\3c&HFF8080&\4c&HC08080&\b1\be1}悲しみから生まれた夢も　世界と君が許してくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.52,0:01:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnDFLiHei-Md\2c&HC08000&\3c&HFF8080&\4c&HC08080&\b1\be1}即使是從悲傷中誕生的夢　也會得到世界與你的諒解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.52,0:01:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\an8\2c&HC08000&\3c&HFF8080&\4c&HC08080&\b1\be1}そう　瞼の裏で繰り返す　この空が呼ぶ声に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.52,0:01:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnDFLiHei-Md\2c&HC08000&\3c&HFF8080&\4c&HC08080&\b1\be1}一切　就在眼前不斷重複著　在這天空下的呼喚聲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:02:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\an8\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC080FF&\4c&H8080FF&\b1\be1}響いて　ただ駆け抜けた　胸に眩い衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:02:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnDFLiHei-Md\2c&HC08080&\3c&HFF80FF&\4c&H8080FF&\b1\be1}響徹著　一心只想著讓懷裡耀眼的衝動飛奔而去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.52,0:02:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\an8\2c&HC08080&\3c&HFF80FF&\4c&H8080FF&\b1\be1}弾けた想いに　My star will shine forever
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.52,0:02:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnDFLiHei-Md\2c&HC08080&\3c&HFF80FF&\4c&H8080FF&\b1\be1}在爆發的情感裡　My star will shine forever
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\an8\2c&HFFFF80&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HC08080&\b1\be1}あの日抱えた全て　強く生きて行け　僕の中で今
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnDFLiHei-Md\2c&HFFFF80&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HC08080&\b1\be1}而我內心現在　緊緊抱著那天的一切　堅強地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\an8\2c&HC08000&\3c&H804000&\4c&HFF8080&\b1\be1}蘇る　時間　この場所で　僕ら絶対譲れない願いを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnDFLiHei-Md\2c&HC08000&\3c&H804000&\4c&HFF8080&\b1\be1}讓停滯的時間復甦　這個地方　是我絕對不能退讓的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.52,0:02:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\an8\2c&H0080FF&\3c&H4080FF&\4c&H00FFFF&\b1\be1}ただ一つこの声で　強く刻んで行け　This is The Asterisk War
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.52,0:02:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnDFLiHei-Md\2c&H0080FF&\3c&H4080FF&\4c&H00FFFF&\b1\be1}用這一聲的吶喊　深深地刻劃下　This is The Asterisk War
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.52,0:00:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.52,0:00:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.52,0:00:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.52,0:00:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.52,0:00:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那個臭小子跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.84,0:00:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}就算鑽進巷子裏也只會被追趕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.72,0:00:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}暫時先回到大馬路上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.96,0:00:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}怎麼辦現在絕對不能引發騷亂打草驚蛇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.22,0:00:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}喂同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.24,0:00:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你莫非正在被人追趕?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.60,0:00:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.04,0:00:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}有麻煩的話需要我幫助你嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.74,0:00:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我們在哪裏見過面嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.56,0:00:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我想應該是初次見面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.96,0:00:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}比起這個沒關係嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.40,0:00:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}要是太悠哉的話 會被他們追上的哦?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}知道了不過我想盡可能避免糾紛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.14,0:00:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}OK那麼往這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.54,0:00:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}喂站住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.80,0:01:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這個女生難不成是「魔女」嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.25,0:02:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}到了這裏的話 暫時應該沒問題了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.83,0:02:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}謝謝你 真的幫了我大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.41,0:02:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}對了 那些人為什麼要追你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}難道是要來敲詐你?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.31,0:02:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不是的 有些原因
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.41,0:02:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.83,0:03:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}嘛 用不著勉強告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.19,0:03:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不過你要是想回去的話 最好還是再等一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.05,0:03:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}歡樂街現在氣氛有點緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.17,0:03:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這樣啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.37,0:03:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}因為現在是星武祭舉辦期間嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.23,0:03:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這段時間警備隊的監管力度一直非常嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.83,0:03:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}然後 控制歡樂街的黑幫似乎也非常戒備
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.37,0:03:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這樣的話也許我應該去其它地方找
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}感謝你的諸多幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.95,0:03:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}可以的話我很想做些什麼向你致謝 但現在實在有事要忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.45,0:03:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}沒關係啦你不用放在心上的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}天霧綾斗君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好驚人的反應速度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.29,0:03:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不愧是晉級鳳凰星武祭決賽的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.15,0:03:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但是你這麼戒備我讓我有點受傷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.71,0:03:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你怎麼知道我是天霧綾斗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}因為你已經是個名人了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.99,0:03:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}在喬裝上還是再花點心思比較好吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:04:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你這樣一眼就被人看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是...是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.69,0:04:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不過我不是因為你是名人才幫你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.59,0:04:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}幫助有困難的人不是理所應當的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.09,0:04:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}而且你看上去不像是壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.93,0:04:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}抱歉 你明明幫了我 我還...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.77,0:04:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你真是個好人呢 嗯 其實我並沒有...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.25,0:04:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}真是的 拜託你也為追你的人考慮一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.01,0:04:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}就是你嗎 那個在找人的小子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.31,0:04:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我們的弟兄對你很在意啊 跟我走一趟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.47,0:04:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}傷腦筋...沒想到都追到這個地方來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}搞什麼 還有個女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.11,0:04:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這可真是令人愉快的歪打正著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.69,0:04:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}讓人一下子就有幹勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.53,0:05:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你們儘管反抗吧 不然的話就太無聊了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.35,0:05:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}等一下 這事和她沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.73,0:05:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}多半是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.63,0:05:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}畢竟他這人似乎是把個人嗜好看得比工作重要的型別
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.49,0:05:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我說的沒錯吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.69,0:05:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}前界龍第七學院序列第七位「雙蛇」關先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}小姑娘你認識我啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.29,0:05:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那還真是令人開心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.17,0:05:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}沒想到曾經晉級王龍星武祭半決賽的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}竟然會淪落為黑幫的走狗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.17,0:05:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這有什麼 都是過去的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.93,0:05:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}等... 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}別來礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.26,0:05:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}危險
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.86,0:05:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}就這點程度嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:05:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}還挺厲害啊小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:06:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那麼我也拿出真本事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不用已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}如果面對的是全盛時期的你 應該不會這麼輕易就得手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.10,0:06:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好了 話說回來 你是在找什麼人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.14,0:06:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}他剛才不是這麼說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.98,0:06:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}沒錯...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我說不定可以幫到你哦你覺得呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你能幫到我?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.24,0:06:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}嗯但是在此之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我們先換個地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好了 到咯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}抱歉 你似乎有急事 我卻還佔用你時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.84,0:06:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不 我才要道歉 完全把你牽連進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.78,0:07:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.04,0:07:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我好像開始有點瞭解你這個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.68,0:07:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}瞭解我?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.30,0:07:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是個即便自己身處危機 依然會顧慮他人的善良的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.04,0:07:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但是 往往會自己一個人背負起一切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不太會去依賴他人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不過 昨天的四分之一決賽...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.94,0:07:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你學會依賴裏斯妃特同學了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.74,0:07:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}終於體現出了一種搭檔的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你看得很仔細啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.70,0:07:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}還好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.88,0:07:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那麼 你能告訴我你在找什麼人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這個 可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.94,0:07:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}放心吧我不會跟你去的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}重要的是你找的人在什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}只要知道這個就行了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}難道 你是探測系的「魔女」嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.90,0:07:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不是的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.28,0:08:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不過 姑且能夠做到類似的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}然後 我需要物件的相關資訊來進行想像
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我知道了 我在找的是一個十歲的女孩 名叫芙羅拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}應該不是迷路之類的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.42,0:08:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是被人擄走的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.32,0:08:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}雖然能猜到犯人是誰 但還不能肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這個就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那麼 那個孩子的相貌和性格是怎樣的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}呃 這個嘛...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}沒問題 這樣應該能行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.66,0:08:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不過在此之前 我希望你能向我保證一件事 可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.98,0:08:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}保證?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}接下來發生的事情不要告訴任何人 幫我保密
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.26,0:08:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我知道了 我向你保證
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那麼 我要開始了 幫我準備一份地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}盡可能大一點的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.58,0:08:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好 這樣就...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.30,0:09:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.70,0:09:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}席爾薇雅·琉奈海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}席爾薇雅·琉奈海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.70,0:10:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}葵恩薇兒女子學園序列第一位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.16,0:10:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是一名歌姬 同時也是魔女...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.72,0:10:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}能夠以「歌聲」為媒介
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}將自身的想像轉化為各種各樣的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}她的能力是...萬能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.42,0:10:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}似乎是在歡樂街北側邊緣的一角呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}芙羅拉就在這裏嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.94,0:10:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}如果時間能更充裕一些的話 就能進一步縮小範圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:10:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不 這樣已經非常足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.36,0:11:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}真的很感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}能幫上忙真是再好不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那麼 我就先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.48,0:11:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不然就要被經紀人罵了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.58,0:11:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}方便的話 能不能給我一個聯絡方式?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.04,0:11:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.06,0:11:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好像很久沒有人像這樣直接開口追求了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.84,0:11:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不 不是的 我不是為了追求...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}只是希望以後能向琉奈海姆小姐道個謝什麼的...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}叫我席爾薇就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.16,0:11:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這是我的私人郵箱 你隨時都可以聯絡我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}其實我之前就對你有點興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.74,0:11:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}今天和你當面交流了一下之後 似乎變得更加感興趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那麼 加油哦 綾斗君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我也會盡我綿薄之力 祈禱芙羅拉平安無事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.52,0:12:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}能推測出芙羅拉所在位置是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.12,0:12:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但你是怎麼鎖定在這塊地方的?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}呃 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.68,0:12:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}抱歉 我不能說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.52,0:12:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好 那我們趕快去這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}綾斗和尤莉絲最好還是不要來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你們還有決賽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.02,0:12:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}決賽是正午開始 不是還有時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.62,0:12:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不 沙沙宮說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你們這樣直接挑戰決賽太魯莽了 最好還是休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.12,0:12:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}綾斗前輩 尤莉絲小姐 沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我們絕對會救出芙羅拉的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}知道了 那我們就傾盡全力在決賽上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.94,0:12:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.32,0:13:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我們去救芙羅拉 你們幫我們報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這樣就萬事圓滿了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是啊 你們也指望著我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.58,0:13:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}就是責任太重了些
