Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.76,0:13:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}姑且提醒一句啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.26,0:13:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}揍飛你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.08,0:13:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}七號 匯報情況
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.94,0:13:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}沒有問題你那邊呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.60,0:13:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}表面上很聽話「影星」也沒有採取行動的跡象
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.86,0:13:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不過聽說那一帶有小鬼在四處打探 行跡明顯很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.64,0:13:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}嘛 掌管歡樂街的全都是些看我不順眼的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.74,0:13:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}所以也無法確定真偽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}若是有人來礙事呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.48,0:13:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}利用你手上的人質 當作棄子也無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.24,0:14:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.08,0:14:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}看來礙事者出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.66,0:14:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這棟大樓原本是一家小有名氣的賭場
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但聽說最近有客人鬧事 被打砸得一片狼藉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.32,0:14:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好...好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.30,0:14:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}嘛 也不是啥稀罕事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不過 整修工程這幾天好像停工了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}停工了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.50,0:14:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這 這麼說 現在裏面沒有人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.32,0:14:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}很可疑對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好 那我們進去調查一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.32,0:14:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}可...可是 要怎麼進去...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.78,0:14:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}安啦 看我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}拜託幫我把下風
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好
