Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好的 那麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不是不是 這沒什麼大不了的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.18,0:15:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}工具是我網路上隨便淘來的 我也只試過那麼幾次而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.50,0:15:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你的手法太熟練了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.08,0:15:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}走走 總之我們快進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.76,0:15:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這裏好像一個人都沒有呢
