Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不管走哪邊 都還是一起行動比較好
