Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.78,0:15:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不也有個詞叫作適材適所嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.88,0:15:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}而且我姑且也試著努力過了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}努力?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.44,0:15:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我雖然派不上什麼用場
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但只要找來一個能派上用場的人就行了吧
