Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.92,0:16:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}搞什麼 沒什麼了不起的啊
