Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.28,0:16:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這是 自律型的能力吧
