Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.92,0:16:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}原來如此 那就沒必要和它們纏鬥了
