Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}喂 現在放鬆好像還太早了哦
