Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.96,0:17:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}馬克菲爾前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.70,0:17:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你怎麼會來這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.08,0:18:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是夜吹那小子硬把我叫來的
