Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}難道你的「拜託」就是抓著別人的弱點交涉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.28,0:18:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那叫脅迫好不好
