Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}對不起 後面就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那麼 好好加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}等 等一下你們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}綺凜 往上還是往下?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}紗夜會選擇哪邊?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.90,0:18:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}雖然已經聽說了事情的原委
