Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.34,0:18:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}為什麼非要讓老子當這種吃力不討好的角色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.02,0:19:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}差不多到時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.94,0:19:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.86,0:19:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}結果紗夜她們還是沒有來聯絡啊
